open-emotions: This video reminded me of how many horrible things are going on in the world today, a few weeks ago, months, years...Ukraine and Russia are just the tip of the iceberg. Human suffering is universal. I feel ambivalent because my everyday life is very peaceful and joyous, and this clip displays a historic violation of basic human rights in a background of war that causes cognitive dissonance. It makes me feel even more grateful for my continuous happiness yet sad for others that are less fortunate.
